sentences.english: The team failed to capitalize on their early lead.
sentences.chinese: 这个队未能充分利用开场时领前的优势。

sentences.english: With the iron fist against the puma vocalist, failed to win.

sentences.english: A lecturer in the English Department has recently been refused tenure .
sentences.chinese: 英语系一名讲师最近未能获得终身职位。

sentences.english: She did not attend the hearing and was not represented in court.
sentences.chinese: 她没有出席法院和参加听证会，也未能向公报发言。

sentences.english: We are not yet back to trend growth levels.
sentences.chinese: 我们仍未能恢复到增长水平。

sentences.english: The tenant failed to pay his rent punctually.
sentences.chinese: 这位房客未能准时交租。

sentences.english: Many of his records in the Negro League were never recorded.
sentences.chinese: 但他在联盟中的许多记录均未能记载下来。

sentences.english: Participant(s) who fail to produce valid identity documents will not be permitted to participate in the race.
sentences.chinese: 未能出示有效身份证明文件的参赛者，不得出赛。

sentences.english: I failed to report for duty on the date indicated.
sentences.chinese: 我未能在指定日期去报到。

sentences.english: It's a shame we were unable to beat Albinoleffe.

sentences.english: The Italian company has failed to finalize an agreement with the UAE, reportedly over a side deal concerning the joint development of UAVs.
sentences.chinese: 意大利公司则未能完成和UAE的协议。

sentences.english: Shell has still not been able to say why the leak occurred in the first place.
sentences.chinese: 壳牌仍未能说清为何泄漏在第一处发生。

sentences.english: He has learned English for only one year, yet he can communicate with people in English.
sentences.chinese: 他才教一年英文，但未能用英文与己来往了。

sentences.english: Phenomenon of this kind of pendulous still fails to get ameliorative in subsequently time.
sentences.chinese: 这种摇摆的现象在随后的时间里仍未能得到改善。

sentences.english: He gloated over his brother's failure to win the prize.
sentences.chinese: 他弟弟未能获奖，他却幸灾乐祸。
